title: Capelo (Felix de Brito)
body: Portuguese naturalist born in Peniche on March 4, 1838, and died on April 16, 1879. E.: Fish of the island of Madeira, Azores, and the Portuguese possessions in Africa, which are in the Lisbon Museum (Jorn. de Sc. Mat., Phys. e Nat, vol. III, p. 194 and 280, and vol. IV, p. 83).
